title: LIZARDMEN COUNTER ATTACK! - Total War: Warhammer 2 - Skaven Campaign - Queek Headtaker #4
description:
LIZARDMEN COUNTER ATTACK! - Total War: Warhammer 2 - Skaven Campaign - Queek Headtaker #4 - The Lizardmen stand in our way from taking the Golden Tower, which is a city that would help us produce more Warp Stone. Queek leads the main army to conquer the Lizardmen, but they wont go down without a fight! Enjoy the episode :D
